Available Tools: create_volume | attach_volume | detach_volume | snapshot_volume | list_volumes
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "volume_id": "string", "instance_id": "string", "size_gb": number }
Response Schema: { "volume_id": "string", "size_gb": number, "state": "string", "attached_to": "string" }
---
Question: Provision a 750GB volume for the machine learning training datasets.
Call: { "func_call": "create_volume", "volume_id": "", "instance_id": "", "size_gb": 750 }
Response: { "volume_id": "vol-ml-train-44", "size_gb": 750, "state": "available", "attached_to": null }

Question: Connect the ML dataset volume vol-ml-train-44 to the GPU worker i-gpu-cluster-09.
Call: { "func_call": "attach_volume", "volume_id": "vol-ml-train-44", "instance_id": "i-gpu-cluster-09", "size_gb": 0 }
Response: { "volume_id": "vol-ml-train-44", "size_gb": 750, "state": "in-use", "attached_to": "i-gpu-cluster-09" }

Question: Create a 100GB scratch disk for the compile server.
Call: { "func_call": "create_volume", "volume_id": "", "instance_id": "", "size_gb": 100 }
Response: { "volume_id": "vol-compile-scratch-11", "size_gb": 100, "state": "available", "attached_to": null }

Question: Attach the compile scratch volume vol-compile-scratch-11 to instance i-build-agent-03.
Call: { "func_call": "attach_volume", "volume_id": "vol-compile-scratch-11", "instance_id": "i-build-agent-03", "size_gb": 0 }
Response: { "volume_id": "vol-compile-scratch-11", "size_gb": 100, "state": "in-use", "attached_to": "i-build-agent-03" }

Question: I need a 5TB cold storage volume for compliance archives.
Call: { "func_call": "create_volume", "volume_id": "", "instance_id": "", "size_gb": 5120 }
Response: { "volume_id": "vol-compliance-archive-77", "size_gb": 5120, "state": "available", "attached_to": null }

